snippet.title: NIMRODS: GunCraft Survivor – Official Steam Next Fest Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Get your latest look at gameplay from NIMRODS: GunCraft Survivor, the upcoming pixel-art bullet-hell shooter from developer Fiveamp. Look for the updated demo on Steam as part of Steam Next Fest in February. 

Wishlist it on Steam:  https://store.steampowered.com/app/2086430/NIMRODS_GunCraft_Survivor/
